### Backend — GitHub Integration Service

#### [NEW] `backend/src/services/github/__init__.py`

#### [NEW] `backend/src/services/github/github_service.py`
- `async def fetch_issues(repo: str, token: Optional[str]) -> list[dict]`
- Uses `httpx.AsyncClient` to call `https://api.github.com/repos/{repo}/issues?state=open&per_page=50`
- Returns structured list of `{id, title, body, number}`
- Rate-limit aware with proper error handling

